
# AUTH APIs

### Register User

POST http://localhost:5001/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
"name": "Rahul",
"email": "rahul@example.com",
"password": "123456"
}

### Login User

POST http://localhost:5001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
"email": "rahul@example.com",
"password": "123456"
}

### Login Admin (pre-seeded, no registration needed)

POST http://localhost:5001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
"email": "admin@crowdfunding.com",
"password": "Admin@123"
}

### Get Logged User (cookie sent automatically)

GET http://localhost:5001/api/auth/me

### Logout

POST http://localhost:5001/api/auth/logout

# CAMPAIGN APIs

### Create Campaign

POST http://localhost:5001/api/campaigns
Content-Type: application/json

{
"title": "Save the Forest",
"description": "Raising funds to protect rainforests.",
"category": "environment",
"goalAmount": 100000,
"deadline": "2026-12-31"
}

### Create Another Campaign

POST http://localhost:5001/api/campaigns
Content-Type: application/json

{
"title": "Help Flood Victims",
"description": "Funds for emergency flood relief.",
"category": "emergency",
"goalAmount": 50000,
"deadline": "2026-12-31"
}
### Get All  Campaigns

GET http://localhost:5001/api/campaigns

### Get Campaign By ID

GET http://localhost:5001/api/campaigns/REPLACE_CAMPAIGN_ID

### Update Campaign

PUT http://localhost:5001/api/campaigns/REPLACE_CAMPAIGN_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
"title": "Save the Amazon Forest",
"goalAmount": 120000
}

### Delete Campaign

DELETE http://localhost:5001/api/campaigns/REPLACE_CAMPAIGN_ID

### ADMIN APIs

### Get Pending Campaigns

GET http://localhost:5001/api/admin/campaigns/pending

### Approve Campaign

PUT http://localhost:5001/api/admin/campaigns/REPLACE_CAMPAIGN_ID/approve

### Reject Campaign

PUT http://localhost:5001/api/admin/campaigns/REPLACE_CAMPAIGN_ID/reject

### Admin Dashboard Stats

GET http://localhost:5001/api/admin/dashboard

### ================================
### DONATION APIs
### ================================

### Donate to Campaign

POST http://localhost:5001/api/donations/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
"campaignId": "REPLACE_CAMPAIGN_ID",
"amount": 1000
}

### Get Donations For Campaign

GET http://localhost:5001/api/donations/campaign/REPLACE_CAMPAIGN_ID

### Get My Donations

GET http://localhost:5001/api/donations/my

### ================================
### COMMENTS APIs
### ================================

### Add Comment

POST http://localhost:5001/api/campaigns/REPLACE_CAMPAIGN_ID/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
"message": "Hope this campaign reaches its goal!"
}

### Get Campaign with Comments

GET http://localhost:5001/api/campaigns/REPLACE_CAMPAIGN_ID
